lvd_readout
===========

trigger matching
----------------
cr of master controller:
    (egal, geht immer)
    2 for scan of slave controllers
    |4 for irq

cr of controller:
    1
    |8 single event mode

cr of acq cards:
    1 or 5 (LETRA)

-blockread
-read event_nr
-read event_info

raw
---
cr of master controller:
    (egal, geht immer)
    2 for scan of slave controllers
    |4 for irq

cr of controller:
    2
    (|8 single event mode)(?)

cr of acq cards:
    2 (raw)
    3 (raw with limit)
    6 (extended time range)
